channel.title: The FM Awards - Mountainous All Stars - Game Over (Actual Super Good Town Performance)
channel.description:
:star::star: All Star Game :star: :star: An Invitational game.
:star: Rules :star: 1. All standard forum rules apply, as usual. 2. Do not communicate about the game outside the game, and don’t angleshoot. 3. Please be respectful to your fellow players. Keep your salt in until post-game. 4. Don’t post in big text or otherwise pretend to be a host of this game. 5. Have fun. :star: Mechanics :star: - Day Phases will last for 72 hours unless shortned by majority lynch. - Night phases will last for 24 hours. - The lynch is decided by Majority ONLY. You will be forced to nolynch if a majority of votes is not reached. :star: Rolelist :star: [color=green]**Citizen Citizen Citizen Citizen Citizen Citizen Citizen Citizen**[/color] [color=red]**Goon**[/color] [color=red]**Goon**[/color] :star: Rolecards :star: [details="Rolecards"] > # [color=green]Citizen[/color] > **[color=green]The Good Guys (But very pissed off)[/color]** > > What the hell? Why was NightX shot before he even began to present the awards? Oh god dammit- it's the Mafia. And now marl's going to say something about hypoclaiming Prince in a closed setup and we're all going to be doomed.... Well. I guess we have no choice. Time to play FM. Again. > > You have no abilities except for your voice and your vote. > > You win when all threats to the [color=green]**Town**[/color] have been eliminated. > # [color=red]Goon[/color] > > [color=red]**A Completely Calm and Sane Murderer**[/color] > > Right.... gun. Check. Anti-mislynch cream.... Check. List of targets.... oh, there are none. All the power roles have been scratched off the list. What a pity. Oh well... This should be pretty easy then. > > You may communicate with your partner, [color=red]**[player]**[/color] at all times. > Each night, one of you may shoot a player, killing them. > > You win when the [color=red]**Mafia**[/color] control 50% of the votes in the game or nothing can prevent this from happening. [/details] :star: The Red Carpet :star: 1. Marluxion 2. Solic 3. PokemonKidRyan - Lynched D1 - [color=red]**Goon**[/color] 4. Firekitten 5. Blizer 6. eevee 7. NuclearBurrito 8. Sarun 9. Luxy 10. Livcus 11. Hippolytus **IT IS NIGHT 0, DO NOT POST**
